My daddy was a sharp shooter.

327
00:30:50,860 --> 00:30:51,733
Was he now?

328
00:30:53,230 --> 00:30:55,750
Will's not a bad shot himself.

329
00:30:55,750 --> 00:30:57,130
Why don't you go show these gentlemen

330
