335
00:31:21,317 --> 00:31:26,317
Oh.
(men laughing)

336
00:31:28,540 --> 00:31:30,460
Will, warm up the coffee.

337
00:31:42,040 --> 00:31:43,600
Hope you like strawberry jam.

338
