357
00:32:52,840 --> 00:32:53,713
Killers.

358
00:32:55,150 --> 00:32:58,434
Good Lord. (laughs)

359
00:32:58,434 --> 00:33:00,250
Oh, oh, I see the confusion.

360
00:33:00,250 --> 00:33:02,770
Boy, she is talking about those trophies

361
00:33:02,770 --> 00:33:05,803
